    <p>Encouraging cycling within your business can have a number of positive benefits. Apart from the health aspects, employees who cycle to work:</p>
<ul>
    <li>May be more motivated</li>
    <li>Can help to reduce pressure on car parking and lower your business travel expenditure</li>
    <li>May mean&nbsp;fewer employee sick days as regular cyclists are often fitter than those who don't</li>
</ul>
